if they gave me one name,

986
01:03:37,001 --> 01:03:38,085
and they all told me.

987
01:03:38,169 --> 01:03:39,003
Nice.

988
01:03:53,726 --> 01:03:57,021
All I did was buy him one cup of tea
during the consultation.

989
01:03:57,104 --> 01:03:59,690
We will speak when my attorney gets here!

990
01:03:59,774 --> 01:04:01,943
So what? I'm an assemblyman.
Don't touch me!

991
01:04:02,026 --> 01:04:03,402
Attorney Kang, where are you?

992
01:04:03,486 --> 01:04:05,821
-Why the hell aren't you here already?
-Please sit.

993
01:04:25,800 --> 01:04:29,303
I want to show you
how you ruined a child's life.

994
